    <string name="about_message">TodoZen is your personal task management companion designed to help you stay organized and productive.\n\nFeatures:\n• Create and manage tasks with customizable priorities\n• Organize tasks by categories\n• Set due dates for important deadlines\n• Track completed tasks\n• Get inspired by motivational quotes\n• Enjoy a quick memory game for relaxation\n\nVersion 1.0.0\nDeveloped by Ilham Kurniawan\n\nThanks for using TodoZen!</string>
    <string name="privacy_policy_message">Privacy Policy for TodoZen\n\nEffective Date: June 2025\n\nInformation Collection:\nTodoZen does not collect any personal information. All task data is stored locally on your device.\n\nPermissions:\n• Internet - Used solely to fetch motivational quotes\n• Network State - To check connectivity before fetching quotes\n\nData Storage:\nAll task data is stored locally on your device and is not shared with any third parties.\n\nThird-Party Services:\nThe app uses a free public API to fetch motivational quotes.\n\nChanges to Policy:\nAny changes to this policy will be updated with new app versions.\n\nContact:\nFor questions about this policy, please contact todozen@example.com.</string>

